<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.9">
<l>cerunī lavēṟkaṇ maṭavār tiṟattuc ciṉattō ṭuniṉṟu maṉattāl vaḷarkkum</l>
<l>arunī lapāva makalap pukaḻcē ramarark kumeytā tavaṇṭat tiruppīr</l>
<l>perunīr nivāvun timuttaṅ koṇarnteṅ kumvittum vayaluḷ kayalpāyn tukaḷa</l>
<l>tirunī laniṉṟu tikaḻkiṉ ṟatillait tiruccit rakūṭam ceṉṟucēr miṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would be in heaven, unattained by even praise-worthy immortals,</l>
<l rend="indent">so harsh, dark sins vanish</l>
<l>Which increase by the mind remaining lustful toward innocent maids,</l>
<l rend="indent">their eyes [like] dark battle spears,</l>
<l>Please go and gather at Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai, where celebrated blue lilies</l>
<l rend="indent">are always shining, as kayal [fish] frolic, leaping in paddy fields</l>
<l>Where the Nivā [River], its great waters swelling,</l>
<l rend="indent">carrying pearls, scatters [them] everywhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
